[I] Diff tool

[T] Kompare is a GUI front-end program that enables differences between source
[T] files to be viewed and merged. It can be used to compare differences on
[T] files or the contents of folders, and it supports a variety of diff formats
[T] and provide many options to customize the information level displayed.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kompare/

[A] The KDE-Team
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

